**Case**

The feminine grammatical gender.

## Declaration

```swift
case feminine
```

## Determining Grammatical Gender

- **Morphology.GrammaticalGender.masculine**: The masculine grammatical gender.
- **Morphology.GrammaticalGender.neuter**: A value to not specify gender when inflecting a string.
